 Deadmau5以5500万美元的价格出售音乐目录https://www.nme.com/news/music/deadmau5-sells-music-catalogue-for-55million-3843989?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=deadmau5-sells-music-catalogue-for-55millionSurej Singh Thu, 06 Mar 2025 06:22:44 +0000 Music NewsNewsDanceEDMElectronic https://www.nme.com/?p=3843989 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/deadmau5@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/deadmau5@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/deadmau5@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/deadmau5@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/deadmau5@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/deadmau5@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/deadmau5@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该交易包括他的标签Mau5trap和未来版本</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/deadmau5-sells-music-catalogue-for-55million-3843989">DeadMau5 Post以5500万美元的价格出售了音乐目录，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/deadmau5@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/deadmau5@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/deadmau5@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/deadmau5@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/deadmau5@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/deadmau5@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/deadmau5@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/deadmau5">Deadmau5</a>已为他的录制音乐目录达成了一笔巨大的交易 - 在下面了解更多信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/deadmau5-world-of-tanks-blitz-familiars-new-music-album-edm-3822566">Deadmau5谈论“坦克世界闪电战”的“熟悉者”和新音乐：“让我们有点奇怪”</a></strong></li></ul><p>据报道，加拿大DJ和制片人 - 真实姓名Joel Zimmerman-与Create Group达成了与他录制的音乐目录的协议，该目录涵盖了4000多个发行版，价格高达5500万美元。</p><p>根据<a href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/deadmau5-mau5trap-catalogs-acquired-create-music-group/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Billboard Pro</em></a>报告，该交易包括艺术家4,000首歌目录的出版和主录音以及他的Mau5Trap唱片公司。该交易还包括对DeadMau5和标签的未来版本的兴趣。 </p><figure id="attachment_3028430" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3028430" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3028430" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Deadmau5-Credit-Scott-Legato-Getty-Images@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Deadmau5" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Deadmau5-Credit-Scott-Legato-Getty-Images@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Deadmau5-Credit-Scott-Legato-Getty-Images@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Deadmau5-Credit-Scott-Legato-Getty-Images@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Deadmau5-Credit-Scott-Legato-Getty-Images@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Deadmau5-Credit-Scott-Legato-Getty-Images@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Deadmau5-Credit-Scott-Legato-Getty-Images@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3028430" class="wp-caption-text"> Deadmau5。学分：Scott Legato / Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> Create Music Group的联合创始人/首席执行官Jonathan Strauss在每个<em>广告牌</em>的声明中说：“现在，Deadmau5和Mau5trap的传奇目录的管家，我们继承了一种永远改变音乐的遗产。乔尔（Joel）的影响力超出了声音 - 他的精通桥梁音乐，游戏和技术，激发了新一代思考更大的想法。这不仅仅是收购；这是一个责任。”</p><p>据报道，这项交易还将看到Deadmau5唱片中创建音乐团体重新发行音乐，尽管尚未透露更多细节。</p><p> Deadmau5现在是最近出售其音乐目录的最新知名音乐家。就在上个月，据报道， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/red-hot-chili-peppers-reportedly-seeking-350million-for-recorded-music-catalogue-3839647">Red Hot Chili Peppers试图以3.5亿美元的价格出售其录制的音乐目录</a>。消息人士称，他们可能已经与华纳（Warner）的大师目录中的一项协议锁定了，尽管这尚未得到证实。 </p><figure id="attachment_3816073" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3816073" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3816073" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Deadmau5-performs-live.jpg" alt="DeadMau5表演现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Deadmau5-performs-live.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Deadmau5-performs-live-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Deadmau5-performs-live-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Deadmau5-performs-live-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Deadmau5-performs-live-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Deadmau5-performs-live-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3816073" class="wp-caption-text"> DeadMau5表演现场表演。学分：圣地亚哥·费利佩/盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>他们跟随<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pink-floyd">Pink Floyd</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queen">Queen</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kiss">Kiss</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tame-impala">Tame Impala</a>的脚步。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pink-floyd-sell-back-catalogue-for-400million-3799093">平克·弗洛伊德（Pink Floyd）于10月以4亿美元的价格将其目录卖给了索尼（Sony）</a> ，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tame-impalas-kevin-parker-sells-entire-past-and-future-catalogue-to-sony-music-3756736">驯服的Impala的凯文·帕克（Kevin Parker）将所有过去和将来的目录都卖给了索尼，以获取未公开的款项</a>。</p><p>同样， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kiss-catalogue-brand-name-and-ip-acquired-by-pophouse-3613184">KISS将他们的整个目录，品牌名称，相似性和IP卖给了瑞典娱乐公司和音乐投资公司Pophouse，</a>含量未公开。迄今为止，音乐历史上最昂贵的目录属于皇后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/queen-sell-music-catalogue-to-sony-music-for-over-1billion-3767084">他于去年6月以高达127亿美元的价格出售给索尼</a>，这标志着其自然界最大的收购。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/deadmau5-sells-music-catalogue-for-55million-3843989">DeadMau5 Post以5500万美元的价格出售了音乐目录，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
