e.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried-joni-mitchell@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried-joni-mitchell@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried-joni-mitchell@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried-joni-mitchell@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried-joni-mitchell@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried-joni-mitchell@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried-joni-mitchell@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/amanda-seyfried">阿曼达·塞弗里德（Amanda Seyfried）</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-tonight-show-starring-jimmy-fallon"><em>吉米·法伦（Jimmy Fallon）主演的《今晚秀》（Tonight Show）</em></a>上的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joni-mitchell">乔尼·米切尔（Joni Mitchell）</a>的标志性1971年《加利福尼亚》（California&#39;）的简短封面 - 在下面查看。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/joni-mitchells-court-and-spark-at-50-3577635">乔尼·米切尔（Joni Mitchell）的“法庭和火花”（Spark）在50岁：“她是我们这一代酷姨妈的每个人”</a></strong></li></ul><p>塞耶弗里德（Seyfried）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jimmy-fallon">法伦（Fallon）</a>出现在<em>《今晚节目》（The Tonight Show</em> ）的最新一集中，以宣传她即将上映的电视节目<em>《长河》（Long Bright River）</em> ，启动了他们谈论她的音乐才华的谈话，包括她在诸如<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/mamma-mia"><em>妈妈米娅（Mamma Mia）之类的音乐电影中的表演！</em></a>和<em>爱情的玛索</em>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3843944" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3843944" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3843944" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amanda-seyfried@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3843944" class="wp-caption-text">阿曼达·塞弗里德（Amanda Seyfried）。图片来源：Gerald Matzka/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>当被问及她的音乐才华时，塞弗里德透露，她在19次大流行期间学会了如何扮演扬琴。法伦（Fallon）挥舞着一个扬琴之后，塞弗里德（Seyfried）分享说，她想在乔尼·米切尔（Joni Mitchell）备受喜爱的“蓝色”专辑中播放“加利福尼亚”。</p><p> “她在扬琴上写了很多蓝色专辑中的歌曲，当世界停下来时，我从那个专辑中学到了很多东西，”塞弗里德在发起《加利福尼亚&#39;的第一节经文和合唱》之前说。</p><p>在下面查看她的封面。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="阿曼达·塞弗里德（Amanda Seyfried）唱歌并扮演扬声器，说萨布丽娜·卡彭特（Sabrina Carpenter）应该加入妈妈米亚（Mamma Mia）！ 3铸件" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ly0kgS2UioA?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>情节播出并在社交媒体上分享了演出的片段之后，观众们对她的表演感到惊讶，此后开始倡导她在传记片中扮演米切尔。</p><p>在她的几个支持者中，请参见下面的Instagram帖子的评论部分 - 包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jameela-jamil-on-how-she-ruined-glastonbury-for-coldplay-superfan-benedict-cumberbatch-3838706">Jameela Jamil</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/regina-spektor">Regina Spektor</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gwen-stefani">Gwen Stefani</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/maya-hawke">Maya Hawke</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ryan-tedder">Ryan Tedder</a> ， <a hre